content.raw:
We are copying all the ROS logs, as recorded by ROS. If something doesn't appear in the logs, then the most likely culprit is something other than the logs and the logging system.

I'd like to reproduce your problem to see what going on. What docker image are you using, and how are you submitting you solution? You can share private information through subt-help@googlegroups.com.
